---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const seo = {"title": "Botox for Hyperhidrosis | D‑Essence Wellness", "description": "Targeted Botox injections help control excessive sweating (hyperhidrosis) in specific areas for dryer, more comfortable skin.", "canonical": "/services/botox-hyperhidrosis", "type": "website", "ogImage": "/og-default" };
---

<BaseLayout {...seo}>

<section class="relative isolate paper">

<style is:global>
  :root{ --paper:#F8F6F2; --ink:#141414; --muted:#5a5a5a; --rule:#E6E1D8; }
  .paper{ background:var(--paper); color:var(--ink); }
  .rule{ border-color:var(--rule); }
  .muted{ color:var(--muted); }
  .measure{ max-width: 64ch; }
  .dropcap:first-letter{ float:left; font-size:3.2rem; line-height:1; padding-right:.35rem; padding-top:.2rem; font-weight:600; }
  .ataglance{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:.75rem 1.25rem; font-size:.95rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span::after{ content:"·"; margin-left:1.25rem; color:var(--muted); }
  .ataglance span:last-child::after{ content:""; margin:0; }
  .pullquote{ border-left:2px solid var(--ink); padding-left:.85rem; font-style:italic; color:#3b3b3b; margin: 1.25rem 0; }
  .icon-check{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; flex:0 0 auto; margin-top:.15rem;}
  .timeline{ position:relative; }
  .timeline::before{ content:""; position:absolute; left:.9rem; top:.25rem; bottom:.25rem; width:2px; background:var(--rule); }
  .tl-step{ position:relative; padding-left:2.25rem; }
  .tl-badge{ position:absolute; left:0; top:.1rem; width:1.8rem; height:1.8rem; border-radius:999px; background:var(--ink); color:#fff; font-size:.9rem; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-weight:600; }
  .tl-title{ font-weight:600; }
  details.faq summary{ list-style:none; }
  details.faq summary::-webkit-details-marker{ display:none; }
  .faq-toggle{ width:1.1rem; height:1.1rem; margin-right:.5rem; flex:0 0 auto; }
  details.faq[open] .plus{ display:none; }
  details.faq:not([open]) .minus{ display:none; }
</style>

  <!-- HERO (same structure as Botox/Xeomin) -->
  <div class="px-6 pt-28 md:pt-32 pb-10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-xs tracking-wider uppercase muted">Service</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-[2.75rem] md:text-6xl leading-[1.05] font-semibold tracking-tight">Botox for Hyperhidrosis</h1>
<div class="mx-auto mt-8 h-px w-48 md:w-64 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-black to-transparent"></div>

      
      
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- BODY (same grid/measure as others) -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 pb-24 grid grid-cols-12 gap-8">
    <article class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-8 xl:col-span-7">

      <!-- DESCRIPTION -->
      <section id="description" class="measure">
        <p class="text-[18px] md:text-[20px] leading-[1.85] text-neutral-900 measure">
          Hyperhidrosis is a condition characterized by sweating that exceeds the body’s needs for temperature control. Botox (onabotulinumtoxinA) works by temporarily blocking the nerve signals that activate local sweat glands, effectively reducing sweat production in the treated area.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[17px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.85] text-neutral-800 measure">
          The treatment is localized—only the injected zones are affected—so your body can still sweat normally elsewhere to regulate heat. Botox is FDA‑approved for underarm (axillary) hyperhidrosis and is commonly used off‑label for palms, soles, face, and scalp when appropriate.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 ataglance">
          <span>Localized effect</span><span>4–6 months relief</span><span>Non‑surgical</span><span>Quality‑of‑life boost</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[17px] md:text-[18px] leading-[1.85] text-neutral-800 measure">“Stay active and confident—without the worry of sweat marks.”</p>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- BENEFITS -->
      <section id="benefits" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Benefits</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-10 gap-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Significant sweat reduction in treated areas.</div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Relief that typically lasts 4–6 months.</div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Quick, non‑surgical procedure with minimal downtime.</div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 muted"><svg class="icon-check" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 7L10 17l-6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>Improves daily comfort and confidence.</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- PROCESS -->
      <section id="process" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">The Process</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 timeline space-y-6">
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">1</div><p class="tl-title">Consultation</p><p class="muted mt-1">We review symptoms, map the most active sweat zones (e.g., with starch‑iodine), and confirm candidacy.</p></div>
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">2</div><p class="tl-title">Treatment</p><p class="muted mt-1">A series of small injections in a grid pattern targets sweat glands precisely. Discomfort is brief and well‑tolerated.</p></div>
          <div class="tl-step"><div class="tl-badge">3</div><p class="tl-title">Follow‑Up</p><p class="muted mt-1">Results build over several days with peak dryness around 1–2 weeks. Maintenance timing is planned together.</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- PRE & POST -->
      <section id="care" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Pre and Post‑Treatment Instructions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium">Before your visit</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 muted mt-2 space-y-2">
              <li>Avoid shaving and antiperspirants on the area for 2–3 days.</li>
              <li>Avoid alcohol and non‑prescribed blood thinners for 24 hours (if medically safe).</li>
              <li>Arrive with clean, product‑free skin; wear loose/accessible clothing.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium">After your visit</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 muted mt-2 space-y-2">
              <li>Skip deodorants, strenuous exercise, and excessive heat for 24 hours.</li>
              <li>Do not rub or massage the treated areas for the first day.</li>
              <li>Stay upright for several hours; expect full effect by 1–2 weeks.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="my-10 h-px border-t rule"></div>

      <!-- FAQS -->
      <section id="faqs" class="measure">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">How does Botox reduce sweating?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">It blocks the nerve signals that activate sweat glands in the treated area.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">Which areas can be treated?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">FDA‑approved for underarms; commonly used off‑label for palms, soles, face, and scalp.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">When will I notice results?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Early improvement appears within days; peak dryness by 1–2 weeks.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">How long do results last?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Typically 4–6 months; some individuals experience longer relief.</p></details>
          <details class="faq"><summary class="flex items-center cursor-pointer"><span class="font-medium ml-1">Is it safe?</span></summary><p class="muted mt-2 ml-6">Yes—when performed by qualified professionals. Side effects are usually mild and temporary.</p></details>
        </div>
      </section>

    </article>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
